 Website: http://www.onetep.org

-------------------------------------------------------------

 Directory Structure

 bin/		Executables
 config/	Example conf.arch for a number of platforms
 doc/           Documentation
 fireballs/	Fireball files for tests and tutorials
 lib/		Libraries
 obj/		For object files creeated on compilation
 pseudo/	Pseudopotential files for tests and tutorials
 src/		The ONETEP source code
 tests/         A set of reference calculations
 utils/         Related utility programs

-------------------------------------------------------------

 For installation instructions, see INSTALL

 Further information can be found on the website 
   http://www.onetep.org and in the tutorial.

